Treatment

set.seed(123)
# Table
table_abundance_treatment_lefse<-df_all_lefse %>%
  filter(Effect == "Treatment") %>%
  mutate(Abundant_place = ifelse(Abundant_place=="mBasal with glycan","mBasal + 2'-FL","mBasal")) %>% 
  mutate(value=ifelse(Abundant_place=="mBasal + 2'-FL",`LDA score (log10)`,
                      ifelse(Abundant_place=="mBasal",`LDA score (log10)`/(-1),NA))) %>%
  mutate(label=paste(Family,Genera)) %>% 
  select(Taxa=label,Family,Genera,value,Group=Abundant_place)
  
table_abundance_treatment_lefse_1<-table_abundance_treatment_lefse %>% ## for legend
  arrange(desc(value)) %>%
  select(Family,Genera)

table_abundance_treatment_lefse_1

# Plot
figure_treatment <- ggplot(data=table_abundance_treatment_lefse, aes(x=reorder(Taxa,value),y=value,fill=Group))+
  geom_bar(stat = "identity") +
  coord_flip()+
  theme_bw() +
  labs(title = "", 
       y="LDA score (log 10)")+
  theme(legend.position = "bottom",
        legend.title = element_text(size=14),
        legend.text = element_text(size=14),
        axis.text.x=element_text(colour="black", face="plain", size=14), 
        axis.title.x=element_text(margin = margin(t = 5), size=16),
        axis.title.y = element_blank(),
        axis.title = element_text(face="plain", size = 10),
        plot.title = element_text(size=10, hjust=0.5), # face="bold"
        panel.border = element_blank(),
        aspect.ratio = 1,
        plot.background = element_rect(fill="transparent", colour = "transparent"),
        panel.grid = element_blank(),
        axis.text.y=element_blank(),
        axis.ticks.y=element_blank()
        )+
  scale_y_continuous(limits = c(-6,6),breaks = seq(-6,6,1))+
  scale_fill_manual(values=c("#b86877","#70a1a7"))
